<lb ed="I" n="0001a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0001a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>宕昌公暉福寺碑</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0003a" xml:id="I01.0001.0003a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0003a00"/><cb:div><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑陽</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑陽</head><cb:div><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">額</cb:mulu><head>額</head>
<lb ed="I" n="0003a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0003a0101">大代宕
<lb ed="I" n="0003a02"/>昌公暉
<lb ed="I" n="0003a03"/>福寺碑</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0003b" xml:id="I01.0001.0003b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0003b00"/><cb:div><cb:mulu level="2" type="其他">本文</cb:mulu><head>本文</head>
<lb ed="I" n="0003b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0003b0101">夫玄宗幽寂。非名相之所<note n="0003001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30304"/>＝詮【史】</note><note n="0003001" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30304"/>【佛拓】，詮【史】</note><app n="0003001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">詮</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30304"/></rdg></app>。至韻沖莫。非稱謂之所攝。妙絕稱謂。<note n="0003002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30305"/>＝微【史】</note><note n="0003002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30305"/>【佛拓】，微【史】</note><app n="0003002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30305"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0003b02"/>言以之載揚。體非名相。圜像以之而應。故群有殊致。道以經焉。萬流
<lb ed="I" n="0003b03"/>競津。法以紀焉。是以神曦騰曜。鏡重<note n="0003003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">昬＝昏【史】</note><note n="0003003" resp="ihp" type="mod">昬【佛拓】，昏【史】</note><app n="0003003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昏</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">昬</rdg></app>於大千。三乘肇唱。拯沈黎於
<lb ed="I" n="0003b04"/>炎宅。用能慈<note n="0003004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30306"/>＝液【史】</note><note n="0003004" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30306"/>【佛拓】，液【史】</note><app n="0003004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">液</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30306"/></rdg></app>流於當時。惠慶光於曠劫。自世道交喪。靈燭潛暉。攸攸群夢。靡照靡矜。我
<lb ed="I" n="0003b05"/>皇文明自天。超世高悟。<note n="0003005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">皷＝鼓【史】</note><note n="0003005" resp="ihp" type="mod">皷【佛拓】，鼓【史】</note><app n="0003005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鼓</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">皷</rdg></app>淳風以懷萬<note n="0003006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">邫＝邦【史】</note><note n="0003006" resp="ihp" type="mod">邫【佛拓】，邦【史】</note><app n="0003006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">邫</rdg></app>。灑靈澤以霑九服。兼遐想<note n="0003007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30308"/>＝虛【史】</note><note n="0003007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30308"/>【佛拓】，虛【史】</note><app n="0003007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>宗。遵崇道教。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b06"/>太皇太后。聖慮淵詳。道心幽暢。協宣皇極。百揆挺惟新之明。緝熙庶績。八表流擊壤<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear>詠。雖智周世□。而方外之志
<lb ed="I" n="0003b07"/>不<note n="0003008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30309"/>＝虧【史】</note><note n="0003008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30309"/>【佛拓】，虧【史】</note><app n="0003008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虧</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30309"/></rdg></app>。形應萬機。而恬素之真弗擾。故能優遊紫宮。憲章遺法。紹靈鷲於溥天。摹祇桓於振旦。非<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">夫</unclear>天縱在躬。量齊<app type="star" corresp="#0003007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0003b08"/>受。其熟能令英風藹而重扇。玄猷淪而再揚哉。散騎常侍安西將軍吏部內行尚書宕昌公　王慶<note n="0003009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">旹＝時【史】</note><note n="0003009" resp="ihp" type="mod">旹【佛拓】，時【史】</note><app n="0003009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">時</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">旹</rdg></app>。資性朗茂。秉
<lb ed="I" n="0003b09"/>心淵<note n="0003010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30310"/>＝懿【史】</note><note n="0003010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30310"/>【佛拓】，懿【史】</note><app n="0003010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">懿</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30310"/></rdg></app>。位亞台衡。任<note n="0003011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30311"/>＝摠【史】</note><note n="0003011" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30311"/>【佛拓】，摠【史】</note><app n="0003011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">摠</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30311"/></rdg></app>機密。翼<note n="0003012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30312"/>＝贊【史】</note><note n="0003012" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30312"/>【佛拓】，贊【史】</note><app n="0003012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">贊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30312"/></rdg></app>之功。光於帝庭。忠規之<note n="0003013" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">莭＝節【史】</note><note n="0003013" resp="ihp" type="mod">莭【佛拓】，節【史】</note><app n="0003013"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">節</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">莭</rdg></app>。彰於朝司。每惟會施之誠<note n="0003014" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">冈＝罔【史】</note><note n="0003014" resp="ihp" type="mod">冈【佛拓】，罔【史】</note><app n="0003014"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罔</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">冈</rdg></app>申。謝生之懃莫報。庶憑冥
<lb ed="I" n="0003b10"/>津。玄期有寄。乃磬竭丹誠。於本鄉南北舊宅。上為
<lb ed="I" n="0003b11"/>二聖造三級佛圖各一區。規崇爽塏。擇形勝之地。臨沃衍。據條剛。面脩巘而帶洛川。佩黃河而負龍門。伐良松於華
<lb ed="I" n="0003b12"/>畎之陰。掇文瑤於荊山之陽。<note n="0003015" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30314"/>＝旌【史】</note><note n="0003015" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30314"/>【佛拓】，旌【史】</note><app n="0003015"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旌</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30314"/></rdg></app>功銳巧。窮妙極思。爰自經始。三載而就。崇基重構。層欄疊起。法堂禪室。通閣連暉。翠
<lb ed="I" n="0003b13"/>林淥流。含榮<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">遞</unclear>暎。蔚若靈椿之茂春陽。嵬若翔雲之籠濛汜。金儀<note n="0003016" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30315"/>＝赫【史】</note><note n="0003016" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30315"/>【佛拓】，赫【史】</note><app n="0003016"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">赫</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30315"/></rdg></app>曜。彩絢光備。覩之者。則瀅發道心。<note n="0003017" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30316"/>＝藻【史】</note><note n="0003017" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30316"/>【佛拓】，藻【史】</note><app n="0003017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藻</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30316"/></rdg></app>除塵垢。悕
<lb ed="I" n="0003b14"/>玄者。則陶真煉和。遺形忘返。諒罕代之神規。當今之<note n="0003018" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB00982"/>＝莊【史】</note><note n="0003018" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB00982"/>【佛拓】，莊【史】</note><app n="0003018"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">莊</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB00982"/></rdg></app>觀者矣。夫功高德盛。徽聲播於管弦。業隆曠載。刊迹流於後
<lb ed="I" n="0003b15"/>昆。所以光宣軌摹。永垂不朽。故姻舊慶慈善之至。邑里感惠訓之誠。遂鐫石立言。式揚暉烈。庶洪因鍾於
<lb ed="I" n="0003b16"/>聖躬。<app type="star" corresp="#0003002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30305"/></rdg></app>津延於先住。其辭曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b17"/>淵哉沖猷。<app type="star" corresp="#0003002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30305"/></rdg></app>矣<app type="star" corresp="#0003007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>宗。<app type="star" corresp="#0003003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">昏</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】">昬</rdg></app>邪交扇。氛徒競鋒。有覺爰興。超悟玄蹤。志懃淨境。開拯塵蒙。於顯大代。長發其祥。景運承苻。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b18"/>世有喆王。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b19"/>后皇高悟。道風載揚。哀此群或。照彼祈鄉。化因道感。道由人敷。愔愔安西。秉德陳謨。冥期幽屬。廓茲靈圖。曾是暉福。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b20"/>慶崇皇居。爰建靈寺。妙契天規。飛椽雲翔。浮欄籠曦。金儀燭曜。功殫世奇。蔚如<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">崑</unclear>峰。<note n="0003019" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30317"/>＝瑍【史】</note><note n="0003019" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30317"/>【佛拓】，瑍【史】</note><app n="0003019"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">瑍</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30317"/></rdg></app>若珠麗。閑堂寂寥。禪室<app type="star" corresp="#0003007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>沖。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b21"/>朱櫺吐霞。翠戶含風。僧徒遊宴。幽宗是融。心栖化表。形寓俗中。靈津匪遼。□照則鏡。蛻神豈緬。<app type="star" corresp="#0003017"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">藻</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30316"/></rdg></app>荃則淨。庶運<app type="star" corresp="#0003002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【佛拓】"><g ref="#CB30305"/></rdg></app>因。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b22"/>慶鍾
<lb ed="I" n="0003b23"/>皇聖。爰覬先慈。永超塵徑。
<lb ed="I" n="0003b24"/>　　　　　　　　太和十二年歲在戊辰七月己卯朔一日建</p></cb:div></cb:div>
